timeline.message:
OpenAPI - Not creating Map structure properly #5863

* Created a new MapGenerator and added it to Generators class.
* Created Elements.java which holds some constants as I felt that BodyGenerator (Element, SYNTAX, FORMSYNTAX) were meant to do this but they are class private and other places could have been using this values.
* DataGenerator
** Changed the isSupport implementation to check for *Schema types rather than looking to the map because adding map type and object type to the map would sound strange as there isn't a default value for them.
** Removed LOG variable from DataGenerator as it was not being used.
** Created isMap, isArray and getGenerators
* OpenApi_defn_map.yaml
** Definitions for Map structures: (String, String), (String, Integer), (String, Boolean),(String, Object)
* BodyGeneratorUnitTest
** Added tests to assert the Map structures described above.
